conbody.p:
PC hardware prerequisites:


at least 1 GHz CPU clock frequency;

at least 1 GB of RAM (2 GB or more recommended);

30 MB hard drive storage for software installation;

screen resolution of at least 1024x768 with color depth of at least 16 bits;

AC97 or Realtek HD Audio compatible sound interface;

100 Mbps network interface;

headset equipped with a microphone.
